<p>A 12-year-old boy, identified by his family as Nico Antic, has died in hospital after a shark attack in Sydney Harbour that left him with severe leg injuries. The incident happened at a harbour beach in Vaucluse in Sydney’s east, with reports describing a group of friends pulling him from the water and getting him to medical care. The death comes amid reports of a cluster of shark encounters along Australia’s east coast in recent days, prompting heightened attention to beach safety and temporary restrictions in some areas.</p><img src='https://kagiproxy.com/img/W54eK0iPcLC-HSrY3uWIZTJjVf8S51IBwHiA_GwtfqhuWcC9yzGHZEmBmcOVYgrxlyCr-NScKI2Wpx5pe0pwujNDKSS7CDS_ejM3PyAmtX_pLS4jgX-9xw8zjMrNmB902DrpCK62JL4ve1PyuOFvJJO2w88W3xz6U4yjlQi4dNIP1m9dlvM' alt='A closed beach at Vaucluse near Sydney on Monday. Nico Antic was attacked on Sunday afternoon by what the authorities believed to have been a bull shark.' /><br /><h3>Highlights:</h3><ul><li>Suspected species: Authorities believed the shark involved may have been a bull shark, a species known to inhabit coastal and estuarine waters including harbours.</li><li>Community support: An online fundraiser described Nico as having the “most kind and generous spirit,” reflecting a wave of community mourning and support for his family.</li><li>Rescue details: Reports said friends pulled the boy from the water after the bite and he was taken to hospital with serious injuries to both legs.</li><li>Recent pattern: Several outlets noted the attack occurred during a spate of shark incidents on Australia’s east coast over the past week, underscoring why officials and beach managers have been on alert.</li></ul><h3>Perspectives:</h3><ul><li>Nico Antic’s family: The family confirmed his death after days in hospital and spoke publicly about their loss as they mourned him. (<a href='https://www.bbc.com/news/articles/c2k98ql703no'>BBC News</a>)</li><li>Local authorities: Officials treated the incident as a serious public-safety event, with reporting indicating they assessed the likely species involved and monitored nearby beach conditions. (<a href='https://www.nytimes.com/2026/01/24/world/australia/australia-shark-attack-boy-dead.html'>The New York Times</a>)</li><li>Beachgoing public: Coverage described heightened concern because the case occurred amid multiple shark encounters along the east coast, influencing public caution and beach access decisions. (<a href='https://www.dw.com/en/australian-boy-injured-by-shark-dies/a-75636311'>DW</a>)</li></ul><h3>Sources:</h3><ul><li><a href='https://japantoday.com/category/world/australian-boy-dies-after-shark-attack-in-sydney-harbour'>Boy dies after shark attack in Sydney Harbor; 5th attack this week</a> - japantoday.com</li><li><a href='https://www.dw.com/en/australian-boy-injured-by-shark-dies/a-75636311'>Australian boy injured by shark dies</a> - dw.com</li><li><a href='https://www.theguardian.com/australia-news/2026/jan/24/nico-antic-12-dies-in-hospital-after-being-attacked-by-a-shark-in-sydney'>Nico Antic, 12, dies in hospital after being attacked by a shark in Sydney</a> - theguardian.com</li><li><a href='https://www.nytimes.com/2026/01/24/world/australia/australia-shark-attack-boy-dead.html'>Australian Boy, 12, Dies After Shark Attack Near Sydney</a> - nytimes.com</li><li><a href='https://www.ndtv.com/world-news/12-year-old-australian-boy-dies-after-shark-attack-in-sydney-harbour-10877364#publisher=newsstand'>12-Year-Old Australian Boy Dies After Shark Attack In Sydney Harbour</a> - ndtv.com</li><li><a href='https://www.scmp.com/news/asia/australasia/article/3341094/australian-boy-12-dies-week-after-shark-attack-sydney-harbour'>Australian boy, 12, dies a week after shark attack in Sydney Harbour</a> - scmp.com</li><li><a href='https://www.bbc.com/news/articles/c2k98ql703no'>Boy, 12, dies from injuries after Sydney shark attack</a> - bbc.com</li></ul>